entries.s_e606ff8b: Is that you again? What do you want?
entries.s_e601f570: Blast it! We're going to be stuck in here! Don't tell her our plans! We'll be finished!
entries.s_cf46030c: Hey! Is anyone out there? Who's that!
entries.s_83c7eb4e: Who sent you? That wife?! She's no good. She tricked us and is starving us in here! C'mon. Help us out of here. We can't do it alone. Our means of escape will cause too much of a ruckuss and she'll just catch us again! Go distract her and we'll do our thing.
entries.s_68f8b129: Fantastic! We'll wait. Quick! Go talk to her..
entries.s_46ea9e29: I'm here to watch over you.
entries.s_46d11795: Oh, nothing. I'll go back to my business.
entries.s_19cc687c: Stay quiet in there! I'll do no such thing.
